  "title": "Sales & Events Ambassadors",
  "description": "<p><strong>Dynamic Role. Real Skills. Real Growth.</strong></p><p><br />Looking for a people-focused, fast-paced role that actually helps you grow? Our Events & Sales position offers hands-on experience, strong earning potential, and a clear progression path.</p><p><br /></p><p>What You’ll Be Doing</p><ul><li>Represent brands at events, roadshows, and live campaigns</li><li>Engage customers through face-to-face interactions</li><li>Support on-the-ground sales and marketing initiatives</li><li>Develop communication, confidence, and leadership skills</li><li>Earn through a performance-based / commission structure</li><li>Access travel and exposure opportunities via events and training</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br />Who This Role Is For</p><ul><li>Energetic, motivated individuals</li><li>Fresh graduates and career switchers encouraged to apply</li><li>Comfortable engaging with people (or willing to learn)</li><li>Team players with a strong growth mindset</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Why Join Us</p><ul><li>Supportive, fun, and high-energy team culture</li><li>Ongoing training and personal development</li><li>Clear progression into leadership or business roles</li><li>Earnings based on performance—not fixed hours</li></ul><p><br /></p><p></p><p>If you’re ready for a role that’s engaging, rewarding, and growth-driven, this could be your next step.</p><p>👉 Apply now or DM us to learn more.</p>",
